edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.viewmodel

Class MainViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
      • androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
        • edu.cnm.deepdive.rps.viewmodel.MainViewModel

  • public class MainViewModel
extends AndroidViewModel
    Manages interaction with (and simulation execution of) an instance of Arena, and exposes its key properties as LiveData.
    Author:
    Nicholas Bennett
